Membosankan./ Sungguh?

121
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,580
Xiao-you.

122
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:20,300
Zhang Zi-qi, berhenti.

123
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:23,820
Tunggu aku di toserba./ Baiklah./
Setelah ini, aku akan mencarimu.

124
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:25,940
Zhang Zi-qi./ Kenapa?

125
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:30,300
